            <abstract encodinganalog="520" label="Abstract">The Adams, R. mss., 1968-1984, collection consists of the papers of
                publishing firm Rex Collings Ltd. relating to the publication of several novels by
                author Richard Adams, primarily <title render="italic">Watership Down.</title></abstract>
